<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَلَمْ يَبْغِ إِلا أَنْ نَبُوءَ بِفَضْلِهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَلَيْنَا وَإِلا أَنْ نَتُوبَ فَيَقْبَلا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هُوَ الأَحَدُ الْقَيُّومُ مِنْ بَعْدِ خَلْقِهِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَمَا زَالَ فِي دَيْمُومَةِ الْخَلْقِ أَوَّلا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَمَا خَلَقَ الإِنْسَانَ إِلا لِغايَةٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَلَمْ يَتْرُكِ الإِنْسَانَ فِي الأَرْضِ مُهْمَلا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>كَفَى عِبْرَةً أَنَّا وَأَنَّكَ يَا أَخِي<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>نُصَرِّفُ تَصْرِيفًا لَطِيفًا وَنُبْتَلَى<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>كَانَا وَقَدْ صِرْنَا حَدِيثًا لِغَيْرِنَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>يُخَاضُ كَمَا خُضْنَا الْحَدِيثَ بِمَنْ خَلا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>تَوَهَّمْتُ قَوْمًا قَدْ خَلُوا فَكَأَنَّهُمُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>بِأَجْمَعِهِم كَانُوا خَيَالاً تَخَيَّلا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَلَسْتُ بِأَبْقَى مِنْهُمْ فِي دِيَارِهِمْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَلَكِنَّ لِي فِيهَا كِتَابًا مُؤَجَّلا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَمَا النَّاسُ إِلا مَيِّتٌ وَابْنُ مَيِّتٍ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>تَأَجَّلَ حَيٌّ مِنْهُمْ أَوْ تَعَجَّلا<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَلا تَحْسَبَنَّ اللهَ يُخْلِفُ وَعدَهُ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>بِمَا كَانَ أَوْصَى الْمُسْلِمِينَ وَأَرْسَلا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>هُوَ الْمَوْتُ يَا ابْنَ الْمَوْتِ وَالْبَعْثُ بَعْدَهُ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَمِنْ بَيْنِ مَبْعُوثٍ مُخفًا وَمُثْقَلاَ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَمِنْ بَيْنِ مَسْحُوبٍ عَلَى حُرٍّ وَجْهِهِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَمِنْ بَيْنِ مَنْ يَأْتِي أَغَرَّ مُحَجَّلا ... &gt;?<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>